title: Tale of Four Cities: Los Angeles - Converse CONS
description:
Tale of Four Cities explores the skate communities within the four cities that CONS Project takes place-- Boston, Toronto, Los Angeles and New York. This film follows CONS skate ambassador Sean Pablo while he visits some of Los Angeles' best skate spots, shops, hangouts, and the community surrounding them.

Directed by Richard Quintero
